{"tid":2490097,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★陳茂波：全力打擊洗黑錢及違《國安法》資金活動","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:47:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70273e5e72c961b61ab9a050c7352cfcadcee3dc","tid":2490097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/JSKUIPHMNVB4PJUKWBLRZUREDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FJSKUIPHMNVB4PJUKWBLRZUREDA%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwFHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=431c2d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FJSKUIPHMNVB4PJUKWBLRZUREDA%2F&h=f3857199\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/JSKUIPHMNVB4PJUKWBLRZUREDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波指，香港經濟安全如沒有保障，就成為國家經濟安全以至整體安全隱患，要發揮「試驗田」和「防火牆」角色， 緩減及阻止境外市場風險傳導至內地市場，及全力打擊洗錢和恐怖分子融資、違反《國安法》的資金活動。金管局總裁余偉文則強調要穩妥掌握聯繫匯率，指過去一年多，流入港元的資金達500億美元，香港支付系統繼續安全有效運作，證明聯匯制度具強大生命力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在「全民國家安全教育日」主題講座，有關經濟安全部份擔任演講嘉賓的陳茂波，雖身在現場但未即席演講，反而如其他嘉賓般，提早拍攝演講短片在場內播放。陳指，過去有國家透過經濟制裁、封鎖，並以貨幣結算作為武器，無非是想迫使別國就範及摧毀別國政權。他形容，經濟安全是國家安全體系的重要組成部份，沒有安全穩定的政治和社會環境，經濟就難以發展。"},{"pid":"a9cf7777e413f39d70e50c1175d0b0c461004bde","tid":2490097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNCVDs1.gif&amp;h=4ed5c0c3&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"8c262e7a35b0b2a83b1b0f548c840121685c35e3","tid":2490097,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"人人表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0164e8cb5721f5689a25aaeb59f1e47a2d16f641","tid":2490097,"uid":299694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite